            <div type="transcript" id="P96-109">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They say that 'time assuages,' </l>
                    <l>Time never did assuage;</l>
                    <l>An actual suffering strengthens,</l>
                    <l>As sinews do, with age.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Time is a test of trouble,</l>
                    <l>But not a remedy.</l>
                    <l>If such it prove, it prove too</l>
                    <l>There was no malady.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
